title: “I’VE ALREADY WON” LOGAN PAUL ON FIGHTING FLOYD MAYWEATHER — BFFs EP. 31
description:
The crew is in Miami for fight week. Logan Paul joins the program to talk about his upcoming fight with Floyd Mayweather, and things get very heated between Jake Paul and Austin McBroom in the middle of our recording day.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/bffspod
